Instructions:

git clone http://github.com/dbolson/dotvim.git ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

To compile Command-T:

cd Command-T/
rvm use system
rake make
rvm use ruby-1.9.2-head

To install JS Lint:

http://www.javascriptlint.com/docs/index.htm
